{"tid":1173934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] 曾蔭權為加大香港人口，鼓勵引入雙非","createTime":"2019-05-27T12:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T13:50:14.000Z","uid":82640,"like":32,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7b97faee41f7f1ad02fda2df2546c1c63e4b55d2","tid":1173934,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T12:58:06.000Z","msg":"有人吹奏曾蔭權，就此特意回帶<br />\n平均引用分開唔同立場嘅報館<br />\n今時今日香港學生勁多普通話係邊個造成？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>任內政策 造就17萬雙非嬰兒 曾蔭權種禍 周一嶽力撐</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160611/00176_003.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160611%2F00176_003.html&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=a6007b28\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160611/00176_003.html</a><br />\n雙非單非學童引起的跨境教育及社會問題，原來是前特首曾蔭權與食物及衞生局前局長周一嶽雙雙埋下的「禍根」。<strong>曾蔭權眼見呼籲港人「生夠三個」無人理，便視雙非童為補充本港人口的新血，更希望港人正面看待他們，致令任內造就十七萬雙非嬰兒</strong>；而周一嶽以「人道立場」為由，明言不可限制內地孕婦來港產子，變相成為鼓勵她們來港分娩。二人的無能管治最終激起社會強烈回響，上街示威不斷，更引起新一輪的中港矛盾，可謂禍港不淺。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>30年增逾180萬人！雙非童撐起本港人口增長</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171228/57636393\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171228%2F57636393&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=8f27a864\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171228%2F57636393&h=5e58a181\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171228/57636393</a><br />\n在過去30年生育率下降及死亡情況不斷改善，本港人口老化現象持續。自然增長（即出生人數相對死亡人數的差額）從1986年年中至1987年年中的45,500人，下降至2003年年中至2004年年中的9,500人。<strong>其後由於雙非兒童增加，自然增長回升至2010年年中至2011年年中的52,600人</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>梁錦松倡本港人口增至1,000萬 支持大灣區以至中國發展</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/250371/%E6%A2%81%E9%8C%A6%E6%9D%BE%E5%80%A1%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B31000%E8%90%AC%E3%80%80%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E4%BB%A5%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F250371%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E9%258C%25A6%25E6%259D%25BE%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%2587%25B31000%25E8%2590%25AC%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=34cca2e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/250371/%E6%A2%81%E9%8C%A6%E6%9D%BE%E5%80%A1%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B31000%E8%90%AC%E3%80%80%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E4%BB%A5%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/</a><br />\n<strong>前特首曾蔭權任內也曾提出，要將香港人口長遠增至1,000萬</strong>，提升香港地位，務求與倫敦和紐約齊名，政府除鼓勵生育外，亦需吸納外來人才。<br />\n<br />\n曾蔭權鼓勵引入雙非，支持直接殖民<br />\n香港人口未到800萬房屋都已經爆大煲，曾蔭權仲話要1000萬人口<br />\n吹奏曾蔭權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2d1a8d0132459ee183b744e4a4a52e9a0d8b96","tid":1173934,"uid":82640,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:00:08.000Z","msg":"掉低負評走人，不願面對事實？"},{"pid":"c9773767e564dfb8e014a7ac19806701b10c424d","tid":1173934,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"掉低負評走人，不願面對事實？"},{"pid":"2fd08dee45eb4a69ed44531fa95a056dbf535735","tid":1173934,"uid":11148,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"c9773767e564dfb8e014a7ac19806701b10c424d","tid":1173934,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"r